{"text_id":166606,"tokens":["The"," itiner","ant"," to"," localized"," transition"," of"," f"," electrons"," in"," the"," anti","ferro","magnetic"," super","conductor"," UP","d","\u2082","Al","\u2083"," has"," been"," the"," focus"," of"," our"," research","."," The"," motivation"," behind"," this"," work"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," the"," complex"," relationship"," between"," f"," electron"," behavior",","," magnetism",","," and"," super","conductivity"," in"," heavy"," ferm","ion"," materials","."," Specifically",","," we"," aim"," to"," solve"," the"," problem"," of"," how"," the"," localized"," f"," electrons"," in"," UP","d","\u2082","Al","\u2083"," give"," way"," to"," itiner","ant"," behavior"," as"," the"," material"," transitions"," to"," a"," superconducting"," state",".","\n\n","To"," address"," this"," problem",","," we"," have"," employed"," a"," combination"," of"," theoretical"," and"," experimental"," techniques","."," On"," the"," theoretical"," side",","," we"," have"," used"," density"," functional"," theory"," (","DFT",")"," calculations"," to"," investigate"," the"," electronic"," structure"," of"," UP","d","\u2082","Al","\u2083","."," Our"," DFT"," results"," show"," a"," clear"," transition"," from"," localized"," to"," itiner","ant"," f"," electron"," behavior"," as"," the"," material"," becomes"," superconducting","."," Furthermore",","," we"," have"," used"," dynamical"," mean","-","field"," theory"," (","DM","FT",")"," to"," study"," the"," role"," of"," electronic"," correlations"," in"," this"," transition","."," Our"," DM","FT"," calculations"," reveal"," that"," the"," itiner","ant"," f"," electrons"," form"," a"," heavy"," ferm","ion"," band",","," which"," is"," responsible"," for"," the"," unconventional"," super","conductivity"," in"," UP","d","\u2082","Al","\u2083",".","\n\n","Experiment","ally",","," we"," have"," performed"," resistivity",","," specific"," heat",","," and"," magnetization"," measurements"," on"," high","-","quality"," single"," crystals"," of"," UP","d","\u2082","Al","\u2083","."," These"," measurements"," confirm"," the"," anti","ferro","magnetic"," and"," superconducting"," transitions"," in"," the"," material"," and"," provide"," evidence"," for"," the"," itiner","ant"," to"," localized"," transition"," of"," f"," electrons","."," Moreover",","," our"," measurements"," of"," the"," upper"," critical"," field"," (","Hc","2",")"," show"," a"," non","-","linear"," behavior",","," which"," further"," supports"," the"," idea"," of"," a"," heavy"," ferm","ion"," band",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," our"," work"," provides"," new"," insights"," into"," the"," itiner","ant"," to"," localized"," transition"," of"," f"," electrons"," in"," UP","d","\u2082","Al","\u2083"," and"," its"," relationship"," to"," anti","ferro","magnetism"," and"," super","conductivity","."," Our"," findings"," have"," implications"," for"," the"," broader"," field"," of"," heavy"," ferm","ion"," materials"," and"," could"," lead"," to"," the"," development"," of"," new"," superconducting"," materials"," with"," unique"," properties","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}